  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a shadow play against a screen or wall. The surface can encompass up to 100 square feet and does not have a singular point of origin, instead making use of all the shadows that mundane objects and structures give off. The number of creatures that can see the shadow play equals your Genjutsu ability modifier. The shadowy figures make no sound but they can dance, run, move, kiss, fight, and so forth. Most of the figures you can creature are based on create you may have seen before.</p>",
